show.description: A powerful man’s inner journey unfolds between the ruins of his fallen empire and his unshakable resolve to return. Here, thirst is not for water, but for immortality, and silence speaks louder than any battle cry. A grand symphony of glory, sacrifice, and the relentless will to rise again.
